_aChangeLog.text: This update solved somethings and added some other things all the Additions and Improvements will be mentioned
1-A Siren sound will play if the bomb explodes and the sound will come from Bombsite B
2-Added a long way for the Terroist to enter bombsite B
4-Changed the Dustcloud Color for both bombsites to this Code"158 149 0"
5-Moved the Nuclear waste boxes on Bombsite A for the terroist to not plant the bomb in a hard position to Find
This verion added some improvements and the major ones will be mentioned
1-Both bombsites now has Dustcloud and fire when the bomb explodes and bombsite B has the biggest Explosion compared to bombsite A
2-Added some overlays to decorate and at the same time Guide the new players in the map but there is not much of them due to Touching faces problem
3-A New entry to Bombsite B to make it easier for the Terroist's to enter the bombsite
4-Removed some unnecessary Walls and Roofs for improving the Performance and making the map More Vram And Ram Friendly
